<HEADLINE> Algiers to Host Preparatory Meeting for OPEC Summit </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ALGIERS, June 25 (Xinhua) -- A preparatory meeting for the
second summit of the Organization of Petroleum Exporting Countries
(OPEC) would be held in Algiers on July 8-9, an Algerian official
said on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
The event will attract experts from 11 OPEC members, Minister of
Energy and Mines Chakib Khelil told reporters.
</P>
