The meeting, decided by the OPEC ministers during their Vienna
meeting on June 21, will work out the agenda of the second summit
of the oil cartel and the relevant technical preparations, Khelil
added.
</P>
<P>
The second OPEC summit, to be held on September 29 in Caracas,
Venezuela, will define the role of the organization in the 21st
century and the new strategy of its members in the light of the
trend of economic globalization. 
