<TEXT>
<P>
WUHAN, June 25 (Xinhua) -- Lightning has been listed as the
cause of death of four people Saturday afternoon in Wuhan, the
capital of central China's Hubei Province, a report reaching here
today said.
</P>
<P>
The dead include three farmers working at a farm in the
Dongxihu District and a 16-year-old youth who was tending another
farm.
</P>
<P>
