<HEADLINE> Kentucky Fried Chicken Tops International Brands in China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 25 (Xinhua) -- Kentucky Fried Chicken is the most
famous international brand in China, according to a survey
conducted by the A.C. Nielsen Co.
</P>
<P>
As many as 45 percent of those surveyed said they had tasted
Kentucky fried chicken at least once.
</P>
<P>
The survey was conducted in 30 major cities in China, including
Beijing, Shanghai, Guangzhou and Tianjin. The researchers received
altogether some 16,000 valid questionnaires.
</P>
<P>
There are now 380 Kentucky Fried Chicken restaurants in nearly
90 cities in China, including 42 in Beijing, employing 23,000
Chinese.
</P>
<P>
Kentucky's Qianmen Fried Chicken Restaurant in Beijing was the
first one set up in China, as well as the largest one in the world.
</P>
</TEXT>
