Beijing University has set up a drug control research institute
in the drug prevention center at the Beijing Ankang Hospital.
</P>
<P>
It will conduct researches on drug management methods and cures
for drug addicts, monitor and survey drugs and the new development
of medicines.
</P>
<P>
China Safeguards Children's Education Rights
</P>
<P>
A number of special vocational schools have been established in
some parts of the country over the past few years to help poor and
disabled children acquire basic education and working skills.
</P>
<P>
Hundreds of children have benefited from the Hope Primary
Vocational School Project, initiated and funded by the China
Working Committee for Caring for the Next Generation.
</P>
