Guangzhou, capital of south China's Guangdong Province, from
December 28 to 30.
</P>
<P>
Chinese students may hand in applications via relevant Chinese
embassies or consulates in foreign countries or the website of
http://www.ocs-gz.gov.cn. They may also contact the organizing
committee for the fair at the e-mail address of ocs-gz@ocs-gz.gov.
cn.
