</P>
<P>
U.S. Cisco Systems Inc. has joined forces with a Chinese
university in further tapping the huge Chinese market.
</P>
<P>
According to an agreement between the San Jose-based company
and Dongnan University in Nanjing, capital of east China's Jiangsu
Province, the two will cooperate in research, development and
sales of Internet technology.
