<HEADLINE> Tyson Stops Savarese in First Round </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, June 24 (Xinhua) -- Former world heavyweight boxing
champion Mike Tyson, with an explosive start, put fellow American
Lou Savarese down 15 seconds into the first round of the non-title
fight in Glasgow Saturday evening.
</P>
<P>
The left hook to the jaw was superb. Savarese was stunned and
the referee John Coyle stepped in. Officially it will be
announced as 38 seconds. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
