Open grasscourt tennis tournament on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
Grosjean, ranked 31st in the world, captured his first tour
title after losing his three previous final appearances at major
tournaments.
</P>
<P>
Zimbabwe's Black had chances to win the first set but failed to
adapt to the blustery conditions. 
